{"tid":1691419,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CCTVB呢篇報導完全冇講斬人既穿灰色衫 反而話黑衣人身邊有把刀","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:56:03.000Z","uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7501e51808bee7734309618181622e7e6bbc04bf","tid":1691419,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"有人發起在多區聚集，之後有人在沙田破壞港鐵站設施，大埔亦有商場店舖被破壞。防暴警察先後進入多個商場，制服多人。太古城中心外，晚上有人懷疑用刀傷人後被圍毆。期間東區區議員趙家賢被人咬掉左耳，據了解情況嚴重。連同趙家賢，共有五人受傷，其中兩人危殆。<br />\n<br />\n晚上七時半，一個穿黑衣、戴黑帽的男子坐在太古城中心外，頸背流血。地上有一把刀。<br />\n<br />\n現場有人說，這名穿灰色上衣、有普通話口音的男子襲擊兩姊妹和其中一人的丈夫。有一名女子用普通話指罵該男子。男子用袋拍打女子。<br />\n<br />\n商場保安和東區區議員趙家賢調停。有人指，灰衣男子懷疑咬掉趙家賢的左耳。有商場保安按著趙家賢的傷口。<br />\n<br />\n這個時候，灰衣男子被人包圍及毆打，有人向他扔煙灰桶，有人用伸縮棍打他的頭。灰衣男子頭破血流。有人屈他雙腳、踢他。<br />\n<br />\n灰衣男子起身，手持垃圾桶，突然衝前，之後攬著一個持著伸縮棍的男子。<br />\n灰衣男子繼續被圍毆。有人再用雨傘襲擊他，又投擲雪糕筒。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察到場，警方在商場內制服至少一人。救護員幫傷者急救，並送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方之後封鎖現場一段太古城道調查。<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢是區議會選舉太古城西候選人，同一選區還有經民聯的丁煌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5dbecf8ce60383db76f6684a/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%B6%99%E5%AE%B6%E8%B3%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%92%AC%E6%8E%89%E5%B7%A6%E8%80%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5dbecf8ce60383db76f6684a%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2592%25AC%25E6%258E%2589%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E8%2580%25B3&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axNToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=e2783b35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5dbecf8ce60383db76f6684a/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%B6%99%E5%AE%B6%E8%B3%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%92%AC%E6%8E%89%E5%B7%A6%E8%80%B3</a>"},{"pid":"3bea9663e677adc053af79c8cefe02a9b7177074","tid":1691419,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日以繼夜，不斷唱衰示威者</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGJCa37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGJCa37.jpg&h=7c66f1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgFwZXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgFwZXz.jpg&h=87967957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzrTtQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzrTtQZ.jpg&h=0233b4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pkpAv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pkpAv5.jpg&h=efcb83f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFSGCKv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFSGCKv.jpg&h=3668f38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpsO2bh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpsO2bh.jpg&h=bfd9d81e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMP54pG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMP54pG.jpg&h=150999b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tN3eXKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtN3eXKO.jpg&h=a59b4034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ns2jppT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fns2jppT.jpg&h=8829a36d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12c757ed525acc7d6011ca03c8ff47054b36bd83","tid":1691419,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"制裁CCTVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bi